description: Pictorial folkloric map showing various legendary adventures of Robin Hood who was possibly a real person born ca. 1160. Includes notes, col. ill. in map area, additional col. ill. in 6 shield-shaped cartouches, and panoramic col. ill. of "The Royal Archery Contest at Finsbury Fields" at top. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image.
